reviewText: One to the best sports documentaries !!!!
Huge fan of Georges for a long time and this movie is more than amazing for any GSP and UFC fan out there! 10/10 for me

This is a very good production which portrays Georges St. Pierre as the master warrior that he is. He is so superior to the rest. One in a million and this video helps us understand why. He is for the history books
This is a outstanding documentary leading up to the Diaz fight. If you a GSP fan is a must have. GET IT!!!!! What are you waiting for? :)
